    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved? This car is in wonderful shape and ready for its next adventure with you. It drives like a dream and has plenty of life left in it! Perfect for weekend getaways or just zipping around town comfortably. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
