    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline via individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Power is managed effectively through the factory M-Variable differential lock. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the dual-VANOS system operates with surgical precision. While showing honest patina consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical integrity is paramount, offering a visceral analog experience with optimized weight distribution and communicative hydraulic steering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Regular maintenance performed. No mechanical issues.",
