    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and runs like a dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready for all your upcoming road trips. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of life here and there, but nothing that takes away from how great it looks and feels on the road. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, comfy car that\u2019s ready to go, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
